# Extended-tier test suite — rare combinations, edge cases, regression bait.
#
# Planned-test backlog. Empty since 2026-07-16: the original backlog is fully
# landed (see the numbered tests in this directory — each header says what it
# pins and, for ports, which retired test it replaces), covered elsewhere, or
# retired; `git log -- tests/container/extended/.scope` has the disposition
# notes.
#
# To plan a test: add a `- name.sh (what it pins)` line under a section
# header here, then land it as an `NN_name.sh` following the smoke-tier
# pattern (source lib.sh; bootstrap; reset_state; aurox …; assert_*).
# Interactive shell flows need a PTY driver example (examples/shell_*_e2e.rs,
# via pty_harness) that the .sh invokes — see 27–32 for the shape.
